Welcome to ACDK.

Please read the Licence-Info in ACDK-Licence.txt.

To install the packages read the reame and install
files in the packages.

Installation order:
1.) acdk_core
2.) acdk_text
3.) acdk_net
4.) acdk_boot
5.) others

Linux
-------------------------------------------------------
After installing the ACDK package (see INSTALL)

(replace PACKAGENAME with acdk_core, acdk_text, etc.)

install it using
> make -f PACKAGENAME.linux install
compile it using
> make -f PACKAGENAME.linux

Solaris
-------------------------------------------------------
After installing the ACDK package (see INSTALL)

(replace PACKAGENAME with acdk_core, acdk_text, etc.)
install it using
> gmake -f PACKAGENAME.sunos-gcc install
compile it using
> gmake -f PACKAGENAME.sunos-gcc

FreeBSD
-------------------------------------------------------
After installing the ACDK package (see INSTALL)

(replace PACKAGENAME with acdk_core, acdk_text, etc.)
install it using
> make -f PACKAGENAME.bsd install
compile it using
> make -f PACKAGENAME.bsd


Windows NT / Windows 2000
-------------------------------------------------------
This distribution contains only project files
for MS Visual C++ 6.
Either
nmake -f acdk_%PACKAGENAME%.nmake install
nmake -f acdk_%PACKAGENAME%.nmake
or
nmake -f acdk_%PACKAGENAME%.nmake install
Open the acdk_%PACKAGENAME%.dsw file and compile the package.

For more detailed information please refer to
the package documentation and
http://acdk.sourceforge.net

Please refer to
http://sourceforge.net/docman/display_doc.php?docid=5800&group_id=15364
for Changes since last releases and open issues.


